data.description: East McKeesport Area, East Allegheny School District, on quiet street. Great front porch, Large backyard includes 2 parcels 30x121 for each parcel. Lots of room to garden or make a sheltered patio. Sizeable kitchen plus dining room. 2 large bedrooms and an additional smaller room for bed, office, nursery or playroom. 1 bath. Walk up attic. Original staircase and banister with intricate wood work in great condition Dry unfinished basement.2 heat sources gas and coal. Come put your own twist on this home. Just add some updates and paint and this home will bring you years of pleasant memories. Easy to show.
